Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:09.04,OP-EN-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}Tell me what's your name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:17.87,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}如果还是相互吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:23.43,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}就在较量中出局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:28.31,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}不管经历多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:35.11,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}如果在漆黑的某处 存在自己缺失的碎片
